deck: An ancient alien who was part of the advanced culture that seeded life in the Sol System, Molochs disembodied spirit now resides in a robotic shell that is capable of manipulating the electromagnetic spectrum, all forms of technology, and processing incalculable amounts of data. Betrayed by his superiors, Moloch now seeks revenge on those who shepherd the human race.
description:
Origin

After his body was destroyed during the Martian Colony mutiny. Moloch eventually joined Prometheus and the other members of T.I.T.A.N. on their Earth colony and assisted them with genetic modification of the indigenous primates. A course of action that was not authorized by their superiors, the Governing Operational Department. When their insubordination was discovered, the members of T.I.T.A.N. were imprisoned and banished far from Earth.

Story Arc

When the opportunity to escape their prison ship presented itself, Moloch and Prometheus fashioned a device to trigger a supernova to open a wormhole to the Sol System. Once they made their way to Earth, Moloch and Prometheus located a suitable egg donor in Nigeria to artificially inseminate. Moloch modified Prometheus genetic contribution in order to maximize the childs physical potential, who grew to maturity within a matter of days due to accelerated gestation in an synthetic womb. Moloch equipped the newly born 18 year old, Eze Thunder, with a protective uniform and supervised him on his mission to retrieve an artifact hidden under the Giza complex. Upon completion of their mission, Moloch returned Eze to the mothership to plan their next move.

Personal Data

Height: 4

Weight: 185 lbs

Eye Colour: Gold

Skin Colour: Silver

Powers and Abilities

Molochs powers are derived from the robotic body that houses his consciousness. He can manipulate the electromagnetic spectrum, generate electrical blasts, magnetic fields, force fields, and energy constructs. A technological owl, Moloch levitates everywhere, can create short distance wormholes and is capable of flight. His vast intellect can process limitless amounts of data, and is adept at technical design and genetic manipulation, which Moloch considers to be two sides of the same coin. His nanotechnology grants Moloch control over any computerized technology he gains access to.

Moloch is a master strategist who is also quite capable of holding his own in battle with his formidable powers.
name: Moloch

deck: An ancient alien who was part of the advanced culture that seeded life in the Sol System, Prometheus has returned from exile to avenge the corruption of Mankind and deliver them from the evil of their treacherous masters.
description:
Origin

Prometheus belongs to an ancient race of beings who have conquered death and mastered life though advanced technology. Under the authority of the Governing Operational Department, the Earth was created as an ecological reserve to manage the development of various organisms and extract natural resources.

As part of the Terraforming Interstellar Totality Architect Network, Prometheus was stationed on Earth to manage and develop the planets ecosystem.

Prometheus and his fellow T.I.T.A.N.s decided to improve compliance in the indigenous primates through genetic modification. A course of action that was not authorized by their superiors, the Governing Operational Department. Eventually, the T.I.T.A.N.s insubordination was discovered and the G.O.D. imprisoned and banished them far from Earth.

Story Arc

When the opportunity to escape their prison ship presented itself, Moloch and Prometheus fashioned a device to trigger a supernova to open a wormhole to the Sol System.

Once they made their way to Earth, Moloch and Prometheus located a suitable donor in Nigeria whose egg they could artificially inseminate. Moloch modified Prometheus genetic contribution in order to maximize the childs physical potential, who grew to maturity within a matter of days due to accelerated gestation in an synthetic womb. During this time, Prometheus oversaw the childs implanted education during the accelerated development process.

Aged 18 years in a matter of days, Eze Thunder embarks on a mission to retrieve an artifact hidden under the Giza complex. This artifact acts as a key that can release Prometheus from the restraining armor that inhibits his abilities. Upon completion of the mission Prometheus dubbed Eze Thunder, Master Man and vowed to guarantee support and victory in the upcoming conflict.

Personal Data

Height: 9 6"

Weight: 465 lbs

Eye Colour: Red

Hair Colour: Black

Skin Colour: Blue

Powers and Abilities

Prometheus belongs race of beings who have enhanced their natural capabilities to super human levels through genetic modification and cybernetic upgrades. He has complete control of his physical body, from density control, shape shifting, and elasticity to size manipulation. Prometheus also has formidable psionic abilities as well, telepathy, telekinesis, ESP and the ability to absorb the life-force from living beings.

All of these abilities are neutralized by the indestructible armour that Prometheus is still trapped within. He is still immortal, invulnerable and physically strong, but unable to use the rest of his powers externally.
name: Prometheus

name: Daniel Fricks

deck: Molly is the daughter of one of Harry Dresden's best friends, Michael, and born with a talent for psychomancy and illusion magic. Stubborn and well intentioned, she rebelled against her loving but strict upbringing and used dark magic with the best of intentions, before becoming Harry's apprentice and learning about the responsibility to use her power wisely.
name: Molly Carpenter
